		<div id="comment_body_64175089"><p>When did I claim anything about Greenland?  You're confusing me with someone else.  My take on ice melting is, "I'm not sure how much is really melting and how important it really is and if it's just part of a long term trend of shrink/grow or it's deadly serious or somewhere in between".  Does my willingness to examine the data from multiple scientists bother you?</p><p>What I do know if we were told decades ago that by now there would be no glaciers on mountains and the North Pole would be entirely water and all<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

